## File Naming and Location

```
src/
  core/
    __tests__/factories/
      index.ts              ← central export
      task.domain.factory.ts
      project.domain.factory.ts
      user.domain.factory.ts
    task/
      task.domain.ts
      task.domain.spec.ts          ← co-located with the file under test
      task.flow.ts
      task.flow.spec.ts
    project/
      project.domain.ts
      project.domain.spec.ts
      project.flow.ts
      project.flow.spec.ts
  shell/
    cli/
      commands/
        task/
